  "optimization_hints": [
    "Q1: Scan 60M lineitem rows filtered on l_shipdate (high selectivity ~98%). Use parallel scan + SIMD vectorization with dictionary encoding on 4-column group-by (4 distinct tuples). Hash aggregation pre-sized to 6 groups. Zone maps on l_shipdate for potential block skip.",
