    "Q6: Scan 60M lineitem with two selective filters (discount BETWEEN=33%, quantity<24 not selective). Combine into single vectorized scan. Pure aggregation (SUM of one expr), no GROUP BY. Use L3 cache-resident partial aggregation.",
    "Q9: Complex 6-table join on lineitem fact + part filter (p_name LIKE '%green%', ~5% selectivity). Build hash table from filtered part+partsupp, probe lineitem+orders. Year extraction from o_orderdate using O(1) integer ops. Group-by 175 rows → sort.",
    "Q18: Subquery materializes large orders (sum(l_quantity)>300) then 3-way join on filtered lineitem. Use semi-join to pre-filter orders early. Partial hash agg on lineitem before full outer agg. Sort limit-100 with heap."
